---
title: Herby Chicken & Brown Butter Sauce with Potato Mash & Steamed Veggies
description: The garlicky, buttery sauce is the star of this meal, drizzled over tender chicken to add juiciness and flavour. Let’s add a
creamy mash to help soak up the last of that sauce and some steamed veggies to cut through all that richness. Bon appétit!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the pea pods in this recipe with green beans due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
